\c 17
\s Nhaka yaManase
\p
\v 1 Kwakavawo nemujenya werudzi rwaManase, nokuti waiva dangwe raJosefa\x + Gen.. 41.51; 46.20; 48.18.\x*, \add waiva\add* waMakiri dangwe raManase baba vaGiriyadhi\x + Gen.. 50.23. Num.. 26.29; 32.39,40. Josh. 13.31. 1 Makor. 7.14.\x*, nokuti iye waiva munhu wehondo, naizvozvo wakava neGiriyadhi neBhashani\x + Det. 3.13.\x*.
\v 2 Kwaivawo neyevakasara vevanakomana vaManase zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo\x + Num.. 26.29-32.\x*, yevana vaAbhiezeri, neyevana vaHereki, neyevana vaAsirieri, neyevana vaShekemu\x + Vato. 6.11,24; 8.2,32. 1 Makor. 7.18.\x*, neyevana vaHeferi\x + Num.. 26.29-32.\x*, neyevana vaShemidha\x + Num.. 26.29-32.\x*. Ava vana vanhurume vaManase mwanakomana waJosefa zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 3 Asi Zerofehadhi mwanakomana waHeferi mwanakomana waGiriyadhi mwanakomana waMakiri mwanakomana waManase waiva asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana. Zvino awa mazita evanasikana vake: Mahira, naNowa, Hogira, Mirika, naTiriza\x + Num.. 26.33; 27.1; 36.2,11. 1 Makor. 7.15.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino vakaswedera pamberi paEriazari mupristi nepamberi paJoshua mwanakomana waNuni\x + 14.1.\x* nepamberi pemachinda vachiti: Jehovha wakaraira Mozisi kutipa nhaka pakati pehama dzedu\x + Num.. 27.6,7.\x*. Zvino wakavapa zvichienderana nemurairo waJehovha nhaka pakati pehama dzababa vavo.
\v 5 Naizvozvo kwakawira mijenya gumi kuna Manase\x + 17.2,3.\x*, kunze kwenyika yeGiriyadhi neBhashani dziri mhiri kwaJoridhani\x + 13.29-31.\x*.
\v 6 Nokuti vanasikana vaManase vakagara nhaka pakati pevanakomana vake. Uye nyika yeGiriyadhi yaiva yevakasara vevanakomana vaManase.
\p
\v 7 Zvino muganhu waManase waiva kubva paAsheri kuenda kuMikimetati\x + 16.6.\x* riri pamberi peShekemu\x + Gen.. 12.6; 33.18; 35.4; 37.12-14. Josh. 20.7; 21.21; 24.1,25,32. Vato. 8.31; 9.1; 1 Madz. 12.1,25. 1 Makor. 6.67. 2 Makor. 10.1. Map. 60.6. Jer. 41.5. Mab. 7.16.\x*; muganhu ndokuenderera kurudyi, kusvika kuvagari veEni-Tapua\x + 15.34.\x*.
\v 8 Nyika yeTapua\x + 15.34.\x* yakava kuna Manase; asi Tapua pamuganhu waManase yakava kuvana vaEfuremu.
\v 9 Zvino muganhu wakaburukira kurwizi Kana nechekuchamhembe kwerwizi. Maguta awa ndeaEfuremu pakati pemaguta aManase\x + 16.9.\x*. Uye muganhu waManase waiva kumaodzanyemba kwerwizi; uye kubuda kwawo kwaiva pagungwa.
\v 10 Kuchamhembe yaiva yaEfuremu, uye kumaodzanyemba yaiva yaManase; uye gungwa waiva muganhu wake; uye kuna Asheri vaisangana kumaodzanyemba, nekuna Isasikari kumabvazuva.
\v 11 Nokuti kuna Isasikari nekuna Asheri Manase\x + 1 Makor. 7.29.\x* waiva neBheti-Sheani nemisha yaro\x + 17.16. Vato. 1.27. 1 Madz. 4.12. 1 Sam. 31.10,12; 2 Sam. 21.12.\x*, neIbhireami nemisha yaro\x + Vato. 1.27. 2 Madz. 9.27. 1 Makor. 6.70; Josh. 21.25.\x*, nevagari veDhori nemisha yaro, nevagari veEndori nemisha yaro\x + 1 Sam. 28.7. Map. 83.10.\x*, nevagari veTaanaki nemisha yaro\x + Vato. 5.19.\x*, nevagari veMegidho nemisha yaro\x + Vato. 5.19.\x*: Nzvimbo nhatu dzezvikomo.
\v 12 Asi vana vaManase vaiva vasingagoni kudzinga panhaka yemaguta iwawo\x + Vato. 1.27,28.\x*; asi VaKenani vaida kugara panyika iyo.
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika vana vaIsraeri pavakava vane simba, kuti vakabatisa VaKenani chibharo, asi havana kuvadzinga zvachose\x + 16.10.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Zvino vana vaJosefa\x + 16.4.\x* vakataura naJoshua\x + Num.. 13.8.\x* vachiti: Makatipirei mujenya umwe nemugove umwe kuva nhaka\x + Gen.. 48.5,22.\x*, zvandiri rudzi rukuru, Jehovha sezvaakandiropafadza kusvika pano\x + Gen.. 48.19. Num.. 26.34,37.\x*?
\v 15 Joshua ndokuti kwavari: Kana uri rudzi rukuru, zvikwirire kudondo\x + 2 Sam. 18.6,17.\x*, unozvitemerapo panyika yeVaPerezi neyeVaRefaimu\x + 17.18. Eze. 23.47.\x*, kana gomo reEfuremu rakamanikana kwauri\x + 24.33.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino vana vaJosefa vakati: Chikomo hachitikwaniri, uye VaKenani vose vanogara munyika yemupata vane ngoro dzematare\x + 11.6.\x*, nevari paBheti-Sheani nemisha yaro, nevari mumupata weJezireeri\x + Vato. 6.33. Hos. 1.5. Josh. 19.18. 1 Madz. 4.12; 18.45,46; 21.1,23; 2 Madz. 8.29; 9.10,15. 10.6,7. 2 Makor. 22.6. Josh. 15.56.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Joshua wakataura kune veimba yaJosefa, kuna Efuremu nekuna Manase achiti: Uri rudzi rukuru, uye une simba guru; haungavi nemujenya umwe;
\v 18 asi gomo richava rako, nokuti idondo, ucharitema; uye kubuda kwaro kuve kwako; nokuti uchadzinga VaKenani kunyange vane ngoro dzematare, kunyange vane simba\x + 11.6.\x*\x + Det. 20.1.\x*.